{"tid":609158,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"政府幾時先肯指配空置咗接近兩年嘅大氣電波頻譜俾現有免費電視台？","createTime":"2018-03-28T19:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T12:48:58.000Z","uid":26418,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dc102175747703aa62f2ce964910274891f6b893","tid":609158,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T19:43:55.000Z","msg":"以前就話仲有免費電視台申請者<br />\n所以先要保番大氣電波頻譜俾佢地將來可以申請使用<br />\n<br />\n但大家都知<br />\n港視已經放棄申請<br />\n政府亦都話再冇免費電視台申請需要處理<br />\n<br />\n點解唔將空置左接近兩年嘅單頻網數碼頻道指配俾現有電視台？<br />\n特別係奇妙電視同埋ViuTV<br />\n奇妙就唔洗講啦 連大氣電波都冇<br />\nViuTV就得半條頻譜 但要開兩個高清台<br />\n<br />\n大家可以參考下各電視台用緊嘅大氣電波數碼頻道：<br />\n<br />\n多頻網數碼頻道：<br />\n一半傳輸容量：TVB 81台<br />\n一半傳輸容量：ViuTV 99台 + ViuTVsix 96台 共用<br />\n(所以點解話收到81就會收到99同96)<br />\n<br />\n單頻網數碼頻道35：<br />\nTVB 82 + 83 + 84 + 85 共用<br />\n<br />\n單頻網數碼頻道37：<br />\n空置<br />\n(原亞視頻譜)<br />\n<br />\n單頻網數碼頻道62：<br />\n港台電視31 + 32 + 33 共用<br />\n<br />\n我個人黎講，最好UHF37指配俾ViuTV同奇妙一人一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c364f8f1319b26cbe992e3d4112bb7da9b28a483","tid":609158,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T19:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8c48e34f4632ec48d2f3ca5e2083c76ef8f06e","tid":609158,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T18:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a49a5d5fad5da89a1258e57a0a52b0153a55c1e","tid":609158,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T21:39:04.000Z","msg":"政府擺明幫緊tvb<br />\n前排先話咩電視廣告修訂<br />\n完全幫tvb搵錢"},{"pid":"bb871f563888a2d5ed22305f49f96fc59c4dfac4","tid":609158,"uid":11920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T22:11:54.000Z","msg":"比返頻譜